  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>Invent</code> means to create something new that nobody has made before. It can be a new tool, machine, or way of doing something. People invent things to solve problems or make life easier. Example: <code>Alexander Graham Bell invented the telephone.</code></p>\n<p><code>Medicine</code> is something you take to help you feel better when you are sick. It can be a pill, a liquid, or a cream. Doctors tell you what medicine to use to get well. Example: <code>I take medicine for my headaches</code>.</p>\n</section>",
